                            </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                          <locus target="#iiv(erso)" facs="003">Fol. iiv(erso)</locus>
                           <desc>
                              Inscription from a teacher to a student: “‘Kahnu, May God keep you from all evil,’ said his father (i.e., his teacher), teacher of Qoma. And he said, ‘Alaqä Kahnu, judge of Däbrä Tabor, called son of Täklä Haymanot, Amen and Amen.’”
                            </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                          <locus target="#54v" facs="057">Fol. 54v</locus>
                           <desc>
                              blank
                            </desc>
                        </item>
